Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:03.79,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:17.73,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心就能神奇地变得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:23.14,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,背后彷佛有你的脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:30.09,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,追赶了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:41.20,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我频频回头看着你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:51.30,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,新恋情的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.38,0:00:55.41,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,是两人在不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:01:07.19,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,展开看不见的爱的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:15.36,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,所以永远不愿分离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:24.61,Chop,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓我只爱你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修的家在那边是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是我跟阿修\N上过的幼儿园吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经从那个溜滑梯跌下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引起了不小的骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美那时候就跟我同班了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来变成不同班\N只有在国中的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两人紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地走在\N前往展望台的坡道上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使走完坡道，来到了展望台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们依然没有将手分开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们依然没有将手分开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}#03 两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然听不见心跳声了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实它还是噗通噗通的跳着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对我的身体感到好羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想从这世界消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，即使是这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是在谈着恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后我们还能像这样\N眺望着这个城镇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你，还有我们的小鬼\N一起出门去吃大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我一定会很想\N让他们看看这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，我来到这里之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会忘记小鬼的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怀念那时候喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起当时\N我们还偷偷的亲热了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说当时一点也不觉得辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们现在依然在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到没有人认识的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听得见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗通噗通的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟一般人的声音不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你的心跳声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下山的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们计划了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人该如何工作赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用存款买车子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人追来了\N就开那辆车逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会先过去等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样，我们约好\N两个小时后在车站会合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后，我们分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（私大联考 必考数学II）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶，冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，被宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（紧急出动 大阪遇袭）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大阪受到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你立刻出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只有你能拯救民众
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一仗不打的话\N敌人迟早会攻来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会先过去等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姊今天在国中的操场等你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我跟你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该也累了吧\N今天就回家去睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如往常的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一如往常的走在\N前往学校的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天好像没发生过什么事似的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我故意放慢脚步\N好让两人的距离不要拉远
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的好热喔，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经秋天了\N还热得像夏天一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，我跟你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于上次的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的，这个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说，如果你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做了不该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经变成共犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是明美啊\N不要吓人好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怀念的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真下流\N居然在看我的体育短裤照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少臭美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那副德行\N我才看不上眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，你在看谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么男生总是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.24,0:12:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛留着这种照片？\N明明都已经是以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种没谈过恋爱的女生\N是不了解男生心理的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛突然跟我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是希望\N你不要伤千濑的心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛变得这么严肃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑她很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说你最近变得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对她有点疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跑来问我“学姊”是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟她说了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是你跟冬美学姊的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前阵子我在地狱坡\N看到有个人跟她长得很像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑着脚踏车擦身而过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我们眼睛对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:14:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在想\N那时候她长得是什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情你也要跟千濑说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的事情一定要跟她说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰唆！\N你明明什么都不懂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干…干嘛啦，阿淳\N你不要吓我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一直对她念念不忘，白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子，你在找麻烦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美丢下这句话就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用她多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙搞什么嘛\N她又不是我妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对她有点疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为我想起冬美学姊的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约好要逃到\N没人认识之处的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果千濑她没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多事想问她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，为什么你那天没有来？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不敢问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得不要问比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑一定发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，千濑，还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两人真的相爱着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，我问你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看，没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在铃声响起前就知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然大白天就要紧急出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在这么明显的地方起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不快点的话，又会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那里，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那栋房子\N我记得那栋房子是空屋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那栋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有辆卡车停在那里对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁没人来的时候\N从那里的后面起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要过来，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会觉得很丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我知道了，我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有人受伤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么\N只是骑脚踏车跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站得起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才好像有个女孩跑过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕，怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是修次？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬…冬美学姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:17:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长这么大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国中的时候还是个小不点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前些时候碰巧在路上看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在想那会不会是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时局真的很不平静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平静安详的住宅区\N竟然会突然瓦斯爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老公说\N这一带应该很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才搬来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过，真不愧是军队驻扎的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灾害救援总是比人早一步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为军人的妻子\N我觉得很骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是老样子啊，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟以前一样沉默寡言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经念高中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是女生的脚\N脸用不着变得那么红吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我脸也红起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热喔，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把窗户打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样抱在一起\N总感觉好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会对不起我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对不起你的老公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是阿铁他自己不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿铁一直没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经快两个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能躺在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体\N已经不会恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是无法恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我一起逃走的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爽约没去的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责修理的伯伯说\N已经无法恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇见冬美学姊的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我暂时忘记了千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了她，觉得轻松了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是残酷…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:43.46,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中有一道裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:50.45,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,难以入眠的夜里总不停的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:59.63,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉中黎明已悄悄到来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:08.98,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,多么想听见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:13.15,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,感受你的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:20.39,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,对你的思念越来越强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:25.09,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,泪水夺眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:30.26,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了我心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:36.50,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍无法忘怀你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:41.38,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:46.91,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,就要结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:52.12,Ched,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬美学姊的事\N真的已经是过去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道，我最喜欢的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，明天我们去约会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终兵器彼女下一回\N「冬美学姊」
